30:15.520 --> 30:16.726
Are you all right?

30:20.400 --> 30:21.845
The guy's a jerk.

30:27.640 --> 30:31.042
Miss, miss, the train
station's the other way.

30:32.440 --> 30:33.560
You need money for a ticket?

30:33.600 --> 30:35.921
You want to help,
go get my money, huh?

30:36.320 --> 30:38.243
Look, I'm sorry. I shouldn't
have left the bag.

30:38.320 --> 30:39.606
Or steal my money!

30:41.120 --> 30:42.963
Lady, if I stole your money,
why would I come back?

30:43.080 --> 30:44.969
You know, it's my
daughter's money.

30:45.040 --> 30:47.361
Ask her to forgive you, not me!

30:48.280 --> 30:50.203
All right, let's go back right
now and call the police, okay?

30:50.280 --> 30:51.486
