going to believe me?

30:51.560 --> 30:52.721
Leave me alone!

30:53.120 --> 30:54.690
Miss. Miss.

30:56.040 --> 30:58.088
Are you trying to kill me off?

30:58.160 --> 31:00.049
I'm gonna take a nap.
I'll see you later.

31:00.360 --> 31:01.486
Wrong floor.

31:02.880 --> 31:04.166
Anna.

31:06.480 --> 31:07.686
You took your own room?

31:07.800 --> 31:09.484
Now you're gonna start on that.

31:09.560 --> 31:11.722
Is nothing good enough for you?

31:11.800 --> 31:13.529
I thought you came here
to spend the week with me.

31:13.640 --> 31:15.449
Did I say in the same room?

31:15.560 --> 31:17.608
Enough people are
talking about us already.

31:17.680 --> 31:19.045
