31:43.440 --> 31:44.851
Fuck.

32:02.320 --> 32:04.322
Sure you don't want one?

32:04.680 --> 32:05.681
Hmm?

32:05.760 --> 32:07.649
It's really very good.

32:08.200 --> 32:09.281
Hmm?

32:19.280 --> 32:21.601
The money was for your daughter?

32:26.200 --> 32:28.202
