33:35.480 --> 33:36.845
<i>I'm sorry, signore.</i>

33:36.920 --> 33:39.400
We have no more rooms.
Very busy.

33:47.960 --> 33:49.325
Hey, hey, hey, hey-

33:49.400 --> 33:51.243
