but not for me, okay?

33:51.320 --> 33:53.800
It's okay. You know,
you can have my bed.

33:53.880 --> 33:55.530
I'll sleep in a chair.

33:55.800 --> 33:57.290
For how long?

33:57.840 --> 33:59.968
What do you mean?
All night.

34:01.040 --> 34:03.088
No, I go sleep in station.

34:03.600 --> 34:05.090
What...

35:13.840 --> 35:16.002
You must need sex very badly.

36:03.960 --> 36:05.000
Watch me.

36:09.560 --> 36:10.925
Watch you what, buddy?

36:59.800 --> 37:01.040
Hi.
Hey.

37:01.120 --> 37:02.884
I'm afraid I took
your robe earlier.

37:02.960 --> 37:04.610
You did.
I'm afraid.

37:05.040 --> 37:07.042
So, you've come to return it?

37:07.520 --> 37:08.567
Well, yeah.
I felt bad.

37:08.640 --> 37:10.244
I mean, I thought you might
need it in the morning.

37:10.400 --> 37:12.368
Well, there's two.
There are?

37:12.520 --> 37:13.567
Oh, yeah.

37:14.280 --> 37:15.361
Oh.

37:15.680 --> 37:17.330
Now I feel foolish.

37:18.160 --> 37:20.606
But it might be damp.

37:21.320 --> 37:23.163
I showered earlier.

37:24.920 --> 37:26.285
So, you do need this one?

37:26.960 --> 37:28.450
Couldn't hurt.

37:43.280 --> 37:44.486
Pick it up.

37:55.600 --> 37:57.284
Hand it to me.

38:07.080 --> 38:08.411
Wow.

38:09.360 --> 38:10.964
Thank you.
Wait...

38:13.200 --> 38:14.565
Open the door!

38:15.720 --> 38:18.200
Sorry. Tired.
Comes with age.

38:18.320 --> 38:19.526
You...

38:22.320 --> 38:23.765
You have my key.

38:24.640 --> 38:25.721
Key? Oh.

38:26.080 --> 38:27.730
It's in the pocket.

38:33.760 --> 38:36.127
You are such an asshole.

39:42.640 --> 39:44.961
<i>It's me.
You're probably asleep.</i>

39:45.200 --> 39:46.247
I'll try the...

39:46.360 --> 39:47.964
<i>Message deleted.</i>

41:23.880 --> 41:24.881
Hello?

41:25.040 --> 41:26.040
Gina's apartment flooded,

41:26.080 --> 41:27.923
and I have to be at a
deposition in 20 minutes.

41:28.560 --> 41:30.528
So, what's wrong?
Other than that?

41:30.600 --> 41:33.080
Dr. Gertner had to change
the meeting to her office.

41:33.160 --> 41:34.161
I'm gonna text you the address.

41:34.240 --> 41:36.242
No, no, no, no, I'm
almost out of minutes.

41:36.960 --> 41:38.644
I don't know what that means.

41:38.920 --> 41:40.001
It means I'm on a prepaid phone

41:40.080 --> 41:41.081
and I'm almost out of minutes.

41:41.160 --> 41:42.840
Besides, I'm not even
supposed to be on it.

41:43.000 --> 41:44.047
Seriously?

41:44.400 --> 41:45.526
Okay, write this down.

41:45.720 --> 41:47.210
Wait. Uh, okay.

41:48.920 --> 41:49.920
Okay-

41:49.960 --> 41:51.928
<i>221 East 70th Street.</i>

41:52.320 --> 41:53.560
Got it?

41:53.920 --> 41:55.251
Oh, I got to go.

41:55.960 --> 41:58.042
Oh, shit!
I'm so sorry.

41:58.720 --> 41:59.767
Oh, God!

42:04.720 --> 42:06.688
You know what, I'll just... I'll
come back when you're done.

42:06.760 --> 42:08.125
I'm so sorry.

42:23.680 --> 42:24.761
Want some?

42:24.840 --> 42:25.887
That bad, was it?

42:28.360 --> 42:31.284
You really want to hear what
I have to say? Mmm-hmm.

42:31.760 --> 42:34.081
Okay. It's well-crafted.
Your structure's clever.

42:34.160 --> 42:36.731
Ooh, clever.

42:36.840 --> 42:38.649
You don't want to hear this?
No, I...

42:40.400 --> 42:41.686
Please.

42:44.440 --> 42:47.887
I guess I wish you'd written
about something more personal.

42:48.000 --> 42:51.641
I mean, this is beautiful.
It is, but cold.

42:52.440 --> 42:54.442
Surprisingly what you
always say about me.

42:55.000 --> 42:56.206
I knew this was a mistake.

42:56.280 --> 42:59.443
No, I can take criticism. I hear
it from my editor every day.

42:59.520 --> 43:01.488
You're a party reporter,
for Christ's sake.

43:02.480 --> 43:04.721
I comment on society.

43:04.800 --> 43:06.450
Well, then I am wrong,
because this is absolutely

43:06.600 --> 43:09.440
up to the literary standards of Women's
Wear <i>Daily.</i>

43:11.040 --> 43:13.247
It's Elaine,
I have to take it.

43:13.360 --> 43:14.521
Hi.

43:15.200 --> 43:16.884
I lost my phone.

43:17.360 --> 43:18.691
That's a drag.

43:19.080 --> 43:21.731
Yeah, it's the worst thing
that's happened all month.

43:23.360 --> 43:25.727
<i>I had all of
Robbie's pictures on it.</i>

43:25.960 --> 43:27.803
And I know you told me to
put them on my computer,

43:27.880 --> 43:29.166
but I just didn't do it.

43:29.760 --> 43:30.761
I'm sorry.

43:33.480 --> 43:35.528
I went to the store. They
gave me a new number.

43:35.680 --> 43:37.284
You could have kept
your old number.

43:38.080 --> 43:39.286
Do you want the number?

43:39.520 --> 43:41.284
Yeah, give me a sec.
I'll put it in my phone.

43:42.640 --> 43:44.529
Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait.

43:55.200 --> 43:56.201
Got it.

43:58.600 --> 44:00.364
I miss you, Michael.

44:10.480 --> 44:11.845
I'm sorry.

44:12.480 --> 44:15.245
It's not your fault.
You're a romantic.

44:15.920 --> 44:17.081
You love love.

44:17.640 --> 44:20.246
<i>It's people you
don't have time for.</i>

44:20.320 --> 44:21.367
Listen...

44:30.280 --> 44:32.169
<i>So, how's the writing?</i>

44:32.480 --> 44:33.925
So good you wouldn't believe.

44:35.600 --> 44:36.931
Sorry.

44:39.800 --> 44:41.290
Is she there?

44:47.520 --> 44:48.885
No.

44:50.480 --> 44:52.721
<i>Would you tell me if she were?</i>

44:53.360 --> 44:54.771
She's not.

44:56.680 --> 44:59.047
Okay. I'll talk
to you later.

45:02.800 --> 45:04.529
Okay-

45:15.560 --> 45:17.767
She having one of those days?

45:18.600 --> 45:21.365
Don't talk about what
you don't understand.

45:21.440 --> 45:23.249
Oh, I'm sorry.
I'm being insensitive.

45:23.320 --> 45:25.322
I'm the one who just took
a call from my spouse

45:25.400 --> 45:27.004
while I was with my lover.

45:27.560 --> 45:29.005
That was stupid,
I'm sorry.

45:29.200 --> 45:31.328
That's the most overused
word in your vocabulary.

45:31.560 --> 45:33.847
Anna, I really need you
to stop attacking me.

45:34.160 --> 45:35.880
If you needed that,
you wouldn't be with me.

45:36.360 --> 45:37.407
I left her.

45:38.400 --> 45:39.731
Two weeks ago.

45:41.320 --> 45:42.321
What did you tell her?

45:42.440 --> 45:44.160
That I had fallen in love
with someone else.

45:44.240 --> 45:45.969
What, me?

45:47.360 --> 45:48.486
You love me?

45:49.680 --> 45:51.880
I thought you loved her. That's
what you've always said.

45:52.560 --> 45:53.607
I do.

45:53.680 --> 45:56.251
So, this is the way you
treat someone you love?

45:56.320 --> 45:57.765
You don't even know
what the word means.

45:57.840 --> 45:58.966
Anna.
Don't touch me.

45:59.840 --> 46:01.001
Do you think I care?

46:01.200 --> 46:03.885
Do you think I could ever love
someone as deceitful as you?

46:04.840 --> 46:06.046
No, fuck you.

46:06.280 --> 46:07.361
This was not the deal.

46:07.680 --> 46:10.160
Now you're gonna go and find
someone and fuck around on me.

46:10.320 --> 46:12.641
Stop this. Did you
tell her who I was?

46:13.280 --> 46:14.361
Did you?

46:14.520 --> 46:15.760
No!

46:17.680 --> 46:20.604
I'm going to my room.
Thanks for the notes.

47:23.240 --> 47:25.607
Ah, 303 just called
for housekeeping.

47:25.680 --> 47:27.444
They had a "Do not disturb" on.

47:27.560 --> 47:29.562
Welcome to show business.

47:38.840 --> 47:40.285
Where'd you get a car?

47:53.440 --> 47:54.521
They just counted it.

48:04.400 --> 48:05.447
Thank you.

48:05.520 --> 48:06.521
You're welcome.

48:08.720 --> 48:10.085
You're not giving it to me?

48:10.160 --> 48:13.050
I'm giving it to you,
but I have to go with you.

48:13.160 --> 48:14.491
That wasn't the deal.

48:15.120 --> 48:16.451
There was no deal.

48:16.960 --> 48:18.530
There was no deal,
I'm giving you my money.

48:18.600 --> 48:20.011
No, you want it back.

48:20.760 --> 48:22.569
No, I want to make sure
that you get there with it.

48:22.640 --> 48:24.085
And you're going to protect me?

48:24.160 --> 48:25.969
Like you did in bar?

48:26.600 --> 48:28.568
These are danger people.

48:29.200 --> 48:30.770
So, you shouldn't
be going alone.

48:35.240 --> 48:37.242
Hey, you can't drive through here.

48:37.320 --> 48:38.320
Watch me.

48:38.400 --> 48:41.051
- Get out of the way! Jesus H.
- Christ!

48:43.200 --> 48:45.328
Watch out. Move, move, move.

49:37.240 --> 49:39.083
<i>You have
reached the law offices...</i>

49:39.160 --> 49:40.400
Excuse me.

49:45.560 --> 49:47.449
Housekeeping!

49:47.720 --> 49:49.006
Hello?

49:53.920 --> 49:55.001
Oh.

50:20.600 --> 50:21.840
$10 phone card.

50:22.160 --> 50:23.491
No $10, $20.

50:33.840 --> 50:34.841
Excuse me.

50:39.440 --> 50:41.044
<i>Please leave a message.</i>

50:42.240 --> 50:44.368
Hey, look,
I lost the address.

50:44.440 --> 50:47.011
70th and what? Just call me back.
I'm on my way.

50:52.840 --> 50:53.966
Thank you for your time.

50:54.040 --> 50:55.929
You're very welcome.

51:09.000 --> 51:10.365
She's late.

51:11.320 --> 51:12.924
Unbelievable.

51:15.960 --> 51:17.883
Well, should we go?

51:19.080 --> 51:20.161
No.

51:21.280 --> 51:22.691
Let's wait.

51:50.520 --> 51:52.921
Jake, I'm so sorry, man. I
don't know where my head was.

51:53.000 --> 51:54.360
No, you know what,
I'm sorry.

51:54.400 --> 51:55.811
I have this thing in 20 minutes.

51:56.240 --> 51:59.289
Fucking book fairs. lend
up eating six times a day.

52:02.360 --> 52:04.522
So, how's Elaine?

52:05.280 --> 52:06.361
Uh...

52:06.760 --> 52:08.205
She's good, good.
Good.

52:08.720 --> 52:09.846
Amazing woman.

52:09.920 --> 52:12.207
How she's coping,
I'll never know.

52:12.880 --> 52:14.211
And Anna?

52:14.960 --> 52:16.689
She would die
that you're asking.

52:16.760 --> 52:19.331
Uh, she thinks
nobody knows about us.

52:19.680 --> 52:23.048
Women have the incredible gift of
being able to deny any reality.

52:26.160 --> 52:27.640
Listen, I was going
to call you anyway

52:27.680 --> 52:29.170
and tell you not
to read those pages.

52:29.240 --> 52:30.366
You know what, I finished
them on the plane.

52:30.440 --> 52:31.885
I couldn't put them down.

52:32.000 --> 52:33.729
We're not gonna publish it.

52:36.600 --> 52:39.649
I'm, uh, reworking it. I
shouldn't have sent it to you.

52:39.760 --> 52:41.125
You know what,
the writing's great.

52:41.200 --> 52:43.601
I love the characters.
That's not it.

52:45.880 --> 52:48.087
The business has changed
so much, Michael.

52:48.160 --> 52:50.003
I wouldn't know
how to market it.

52:50.080 --> 52:52.242
I don't even recognize
our own house anymore.

52:52.760 --> 52:55.240
I'm selling self-help
cookbooks by reality stars.

52:56.240 --> 52:57.320
Somebody else will print it.

52:57.360 --> 52:58.407
It'll make a fortune.

52:58.480 --> 53:00.164
We'll be jealous as hell.

53:01.320 --> 53:03.800
I really am sorry, Michael.
I do have this thing.

53:04.760 --> 53:05.807
Call me when you're back.

53:05.880 --> 53:07.564
Don't lie to me,
you son of a bitch!

53:08.520 --> 53:09.521
I'm a son of a bitch?

53:09.600 --> 53:11.284
I've known you how long?

53:11.360 --> 53:13.408
How long, Jake? Don't
you dare lie to me.

53:26.280 --> 53:27.611
Okay-

53:28.920 --> 53:31.127
Your first book,
stunning.

53:32.600 --> 53:36.047
It was cruel and raw.
No pity, no shame.

53:36.520 --> 53:38.409
God, I used to proofread
your galleys sweating,

53:38.480 --> 53:39.845
it was so fucking brave.

53:42.200 --> 53:43.440
